{"tid":2428835,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"上學年2,120大專生退學 理大佔逾500人八大中最多","createTime":"2021-03-02T00:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:25:41.000Z","uid":230530,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a5091c60e36241010ee8c9adb8d1bcefeea4983f","tid":2428835,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:34:59.000Z","msg":"大學教育資助委員會（教資會）發表最新年報，2019/20學年共有2,120名學生退學，當中1,804人正修讀學士學位課程，較上一學年增加約15%，亦是創16年新高；當中理工大學整體退學人數超過500名，為八大院校的榜首。<br />\n<br />\n根據最新數據顯示，在2019/20學年，修讀學士學位的退學人數為1,804人；修讀副學位、研究院修課課程的退學數字分別有280及37人。當中理工大學整體退學人數為505名，較18/19學年的359名飆升40.6%，為八間大學中退學人數最多；其次為城市大學，362名學生選擇退學；港大及中大退學人數亦超過300名，分別有357名及311名，科大退學人數則上升35%至207人，浸大及嶺大則分別有160名及68名學生退學。"},{"pid":"cf1bc9e9b8279734464d399bae31e475ef21fedb","tid":2428835,"uid":260694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:36:02.000Z","msg":"支生逃亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52216a4b2661e22e4616c84096b7619921ecc471","tid":2428835,"uid":51200,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"cf1bc9e9b8279734464d399bae31e475ef21fedb","tid":2428835,"uid":260694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:36:02.000Z","msg":"支生逃亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:49:09.000Z","msg":"年年都有，唔排除一部分走難<br />\n但應該有唔少係搏re jupas <br />\n人數一年少過一年<br />\n下年20分都有hku offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2212e95422073feeb44500a286617629ad0e60","tid":2428835,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52216a4b2661e22e4616c84096b7619921ecc471","tid":2428835,"uid":51200,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"cf1bc9e9b8279734464d399bae31e475ef21fedb","tid":2428835,"uid":260694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:36:02.000Z","msg":"支生逃亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"re